README - BC Simple Subscription
===============================


What is the BC Simple Subscription extension?
=============================================

Provides for Simple User Subscription Shop Solution

eZ Network Guidelines label this extension as type 'D'.


Version
=======

The current version of BC Simple Subscription is 1.0.1.
Last Updated: October 30, 2007

You can find details about changes for this
version in doc/changelogs/CHANGELOG-1.0.1


