Requirements
============

The following requirements exists for using the extension:

o  eZ publish version:

   Make sure you use eZ publish version 3.8 or higher.

o  PHP version:

   Make sure you have PHP 4.4.x or higher.

o  eZ publish must be reachable from the internet:

   Make sure you have installed eZ publish on a webserver
   that is reachable by users on the internet.


Installation
============

Details on installing the extension located in the file doc/INSTALL.


